description: If you’re jonesing fo a scrumptious warm & toasted sandwich on the streets of Norman, Momma Oaktree’s Kitchen is just the truck for you. They’re serving up savory sandwiches made exclusively with the freshest ingredients, and it’s no wonder they’re Oklahoma’s favorite lunchtime munch. Their selection includes the famous Katie Bug (with turkey, crisp bacon, swiss, and fresh avocado), the Pulled Pork (kicked up with an awesome hot sauce), the Dougie Doug (with roast beef, pepper jack, green chili, and creamy chipotle mayo), and these are only a few.  And before you go, be sure to dig into the tasty fresh-baked goodies; Brownies, Cookies, Cinnamon Rolls, all make for the perfect sweet treat. For all this and more, make your way to Momma Oaktree’s Kitchen for a most delicious meal.
name: Momma Oaktree's Kitchen
